data.description: Recently remodeled gem offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. 3 bed 2 bath with a flex room, can be additional bed room, movie room, office, options are endless. Enjoy a nice night on the 40 foot covered porch.  Bryant School District, bus picks up at driveway. 26' round above-ground pool with deck, perfect for summer relaxation. 20 X 22-foot shop with concrete floor and power for your hobbies or additional storage. 40-foot conex for even more storage space. Conveniently located within 15 minutes of Bryant or the Outlets. New septic system in 2018; New HVAC 2018 ; New Roof 2022; New hot water heater 2020. 2 Refrigerators, kitchen table, washer & dryer, master TV, electric fireplace, swing set & trampoline all convey with property.
